spec_data.Name: perl-ExtUtils-ParseXS
spec_data.Description:
ExtUtils::ParseXS will compile XS code into C code by embedding the
constructs necessary to let C functions manipulate Perl values and creates
the glue necessary to let Perl access those functions.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 01 Aug 2017 03:32:58 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Module and a script for converting Perl XS code into C code
